[I] A cross-platform Graphic API

[T] SDL_image is an image loading library that is used with the SDL
[T] library, and almost as portable. It allows a programmer to use multiple
[T] image formats without having to code all the loading and conversion
[T] algorithms themselves.

[U] https://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/

